data.description: MOVE IN READY!!! Beautiful home with fresh paint in Middleton Idaho. Nice layout which makes the home feel bigger. Wood Stove with a stone mantel just waiting for you. Newer hot water heater and more. Enjoy the back yard with a fire pit, garden area with raised flower beds. Master bedroom has ceiling fan, SHED STAYS. Come enjoy Middleton Idaho and this home. 4TH BEDROOM / Utility room, or use as an office.
